description:
The next time the family is suiting up for the elements, outfit your baby in these cozy, water-resistant winter pants. The wind-cutting shell reverses to a soft, high-pile fleece, giving you options.Reversible design with pockets on both sides.Shell is recycled polyester with a PFC-free DWR finish.High-pile plush fleece.Elasticized waist allows for easy on/off.Gusseted crotch fits over a diaper.Spandex binding at ankle holds shape and seals out chill.

